    <!-- ==========================================
         WHY YOUR SUPPORT MATTERS
         ========================================== -->
    <section class="section section--soft" id="why-support" aria-labelledby="why-support-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-width">
          <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-label">Why It Matters</span>
            <h2 id="why-support-heading">Your generosity makes this work possible</h2>
          </div>

          <p class="lead">
            Behind every resource we create, every family we support, and every story we help
            preserve, there are people like you who believe that identity and dignity are worth
            protecting. Your support allows us to reach more families, develop meaningful tools,
            and build a community where no one navigating memory loss has to feel alone.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every contribution &mdash; no matter the size &mdash; has a direct impact. It funds
            the creation of memory books, family guides, and connection programs. It supports
            outreach to communities that need us most. And it sends a powerful message to every
            individual and family we serve: you still matter, and we are here.
          </p>
        </div><!-- /.content-width -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->
    </section>


